flowchart TD
    NativeZip["Native X archive zip"]
    BrowserExtract["Browser extractor<br/>normalize + upload extracted JSON"]
    Community["Community Archive"]
    Import["`twitter_import.py`<br/>sanitize ids, apply filters, split likes,<br/>upsert `input.parquet`, write imports manifest"]
    Input[("`input.parquet` + `meta.json`")]
    Likes["Optional sibling dataset<br/>`<dataset>-likes`"]
    Embed["`embed.py`<br/>contextual embeddings"]
    EmbArtifacts[("`embeddings/*.h5` + `*.json`")]
    DisplayUmap["`umapper.py`<br/>2D display UMAP"]
    ClusterUmap["`umapper.py`<br/>clustering manifold"]
    Hierarchy["`build_hierarchy.py`<br/>PLSCAN hierarchy"]
    Labels["`toponymy_labels.py`<br/>name hierarchy + audit loop"]
    Scope["`scope_runner.run_scope()`<br/>materialize serving parquet,<br/>validate contract, export LanceDB"]
    ScopeArtifacts[("`scopes/*.json` + `*-input.parquet`")]
    DatasetDB[("dataset `lancedb/`")]
    CatalogDB[("catalog `lancedb/`<br/>`system__datasets` + `system__scopes`")]
    Links["`build_links_graph.py`"]
    LinkArtifacts[("`links/*.parquet` + `meta.json`")]
    Explore["Explore UI + search + graph routes"]

    NativeZip --> BrowserExtract --> Import
    Community --> Import
    Import --> Input
    Import -.->|if include likes| Likes

    Input --> Embed --> EmbArtifacts
    EmbArtifacts --> DisplayUmap
    EmbArtifacts --> ClusterUmap
    ClusterUmap --> Hierarchy --> Labels

    Input --> Scope
    DisplayUmap --> Scope
    Labels --> Scope

    Scope --> ScopeArtifacts
    Scope --> DatasetDB
    Scope --> CatalogDB

    Input --> Links
    Links --> LinkArtifacts
    LinkArtifacts --> Explore
    DatasetDB --> Explore
    CatalogDB --> Explore
